description: This file is the entry point for a React web application. It imports React and ReactDOM, along with styling and the main App component, then renders the App component inside a DOM element with id 'root' using React.StrictMode.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root React DOM node for rendering React components.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders React elements into the root DOM node.
